title: Expectations Dictate Results
itunes:title: Expectations Dictate Results
description:
Episode 210 - In this episode I talk about how teachers expectations of their students will dictate their students results. If that is the case then how else can expectations dictate results in our lives? The fact is we grow into the expectations that are set for us from an early age and we can either succumb to them or break through them. Listen as I dive into this topic much more in depth.
